{"id":"812080882692259840","type":"text","timestamp":1774460680,"post_url":"https://www.tumblr.com/blog/view/goodtransgirl/812080882692259840","is_reblog":true,"added_content":false,"tags":[],"reblog_ready":false,"body":"<p><a class=\"tumblr_blog\" href=\"https://www.tumblr.com/blog/view/sapphic-dice/810495231022825472\">sapphic-dice</a>:</p><blockquote><p><a class=\"tumblr_blog\" href=\"https://www.tumblr.com/blog/view/anjeriouskharne/810494845011558400\">anjeriouskharne</a>:</p><blockquote><p><a class=\"tumblr_blog\" href=\"https://www.tumblr.com/blog/view/sapphic-dice/810489535374016513\">sapphic-dice</a>:</p><blockquote><p><a class=\"tumblr_blog\" href=\"https://www.tumblr.com/blog/view/sapphic-dice/810488589711491072\">sapphic-dice</a>:</p><blockquote><p>Girlfriend count has risen to 3.</p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p>Fuck…</p></blockquote><p>And I’m not the one in charge of any of my relationships.</p><p>My girlfriends all independently saw me, grabbed me, and I’m just here now I guess. </p></blockquote><p>I too, have 3&hellip; and theres chances it rises to 4 soon&hellip; many developments on the poly loser tgirl front. Many indeed</p></blockquote><p>*high five!* </p></blockquote>","trail":[{"blog":{"name":"sapphic-dice"},"post":{"id":"810488589711491072"}},{"blog":{"name":"sapphic-dice"},"post":{"id":"810489535374016513"}},{"blog":{"name":"anjeriouskharne"},"post":{"id":"810494845011558400"}},{"blog":{"name":"sapphic-dice"},"post":{"id":"810495231022825472"}}],"baseline_notes":604,"baseline_ts":1774705101.464}